<OpenOfficeDictionaries>
	<!--
		Most dictionaries below pull the .aff + .dic files directly from
		https://github.com/LibreOffice/dictionaries (master branch) - that is the
		canonical upstream and the URLs are stable. Each <Dictionary> may carry
		multiple <DownloadLink> entries; every link is fetched and saved by URL
		basename into the dictionaries folder, so a single dictionary maps to its
		own set of files (one dictionary per download - no bundling).

		Where LibreOffice does not ship a dictionary (Basque, Irish, Latin, Lower
		Sorbian, Vietnamese+English, etc.) the original .oxt / .zip URL is kept;
		those are downloaded and extracted as before.
	-->
